name: Burner #1: FOMO Burner
description:
Life: 6, Speed: 5, Damage: 1

Behavior: The FOMO Burner is the most common Burner enemy in Tezuru Challenge. They just run forward, trying to get whatever they can and copping the lives of your Tezurus.

Utility: Collect all 5 Burners to add +1 Damage to all your Tezurus.
